        "46": {
          "id": "46",
          "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
          "text": "A deal well done. Congratulations all around.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "44",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "1": {
              "id": "1",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What now?",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "44",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "27": {
                  "id": "27",
                  "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                  "text": "Hm. I redecorate, I think. This place could do with some Zhentarim banners. Then we prepare.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "44",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {}
                }
              }
            },
            "34": {
              "id": "34",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I'm still not entirely clear what I get out of it.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "28",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "19": {
                  "id": "19",
                  "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                  "text": "Besides that dragon's hoard you got from the Counting House?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "28",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "44": {
                      "id": "44",
                      "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                      "text": "When it comes time to fight the Absolute, you'll have a private army at your beck and call. With a newly-minted Sword-captain at its head, I suspect.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: 'Sword captain' is a reference to herself - a faux-humble 'yours truly', as she's sure she'll get a promotion",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [
                        "LOW_Guildhall_State_ZhentWillHelpEND"
                      ],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "28",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "38": {
                          "id": "38",
                          "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                          "text": "The Network has been looking for a toe-hold in this city for years, and I just gave them the whole damn leg-up.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "28",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "8": {
                              "id": "8",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I did.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "28",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "48": {
                                  "id": "48",
                                  "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                                  "text": "It's been a fruitful partnership, no doubt. Without Nine-Fingers clogging up the works, the Zhentarim have a clear run of the cities on the coast now.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "28",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "51": {
                              "id": "51",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "And you only had to collaborate with a death-cult to do it. Your superiors won't mind?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "2",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "21": {
                                  "id": "21",
                                  "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                                  "text": "I did what I was trained to - spotted the balance of power shifting, and nudged where I needed to make sure it fell our way.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "28": {
                                      "id": "28",
                                      "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                                      "text": "You benefit too, don't forget. Go pick a fight with this god - we'll be there when you need us.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "2": {
                                          "id": "2",
                                          "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                                          "text": "You have my word.",
                                          "context": "NodeContext: Faux-formality, with a little bow. She does mean it, but she's toying with us a little bit - we've just seen firsthand that she has no problem going back on her word.",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "35": {
                              "id": "35",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Why does the Zhentarim care so much about Baldur's Gate?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "2",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "24": {
                                  "id": "24",
                                  "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                                  "text": "Trade, why else? That gap-handed wench and her Guild held their monopoly for far too long.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "2",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "45": {
                                      "id": "45",
                                      "speaker": "Roah Moonglow",
                                      "text": "Now the Guild can become a Zhent operation - and we'll have your back when the battle-horns start blowing.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "2",
